data.description: AMAZING 2 story home built in 2014 with 3 Bedrooms, 3 Baths w/FULL bed and bath downstairs! This home has the biggest lot in the subdivision and on a corner with low maintenance desert landscaping & multiple shade trees! Interior features a BRIGHT & OPEN floor plan with 16" tile floors throughout downstairs & in all wet areas! Large kitchen with Island/breakfast bar, Granite counters, extended cabinets with work space, pantry, & black appliances. H2O softener & filtration, Good size family room with ceiling fan & dining area. Upstairs has an enormous loft separating the primary bedroom from the secondary bedroom. HUGE primary bedroom with sitting area, DUAL walk-in closets & large bathroom with separate tub/shower, dual sinks, & make-up counter! Large secondary bedroom upstairs with ceiling fan & attached bath! Fantastic backyard that has artificial grass & endless opportunities to make it your own. This gorgeous home is nestled in a GATED community with a park & playground! MUST SEE!
